name: Fetch, Boy
description:
You're dead, but that won't stop you from playing fetch! 
Use 'Q' and 'W' to control your body and jump for bones, avoiding falling over or crashing into any pipes in the process!
This game, inspired by a fusion of QWOP and Flappy Bird, hopes to provide a challenge while being silly and fun!
